.service.service-tanning
  h1.service-title Tanning

  .service-container.service-container--closed
    svg.service-image(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink', viewbox='0 0 1920 1200', preserveaspectratio='xMidYMid slice')
      defs
        clippath#tanningPath
          polygon.clip(points='0, 1200 0, 0 1920, 0 1920, 1200')

      image(clip-path='url(#tanningPath)', width='1920', height='1200', xlink:href='img/categories/tanning.jpg')

    .grid
      .service-content
        .service-body
          i.service-btn-close

          .service-caption
            .service-caption-description
              p.
                On the ground floor you will find our bright &amp; vibrant tanning
                lounge. Our stand up or lie down sunbeds are regularly maintained,
                retubed and kept to the highest standard of cleanliness.

              p.
                With private rooms, complimentary toiletries and robes all set in
                a relaxed atmosphere, our experienced and friendly staff are always
                on hand to advise you on how to achieve and maintain your perfect
                tan.

              p.
                Sunbed prices are £1.50 for 3 minutes or take advantage of our
                special offers. Sunbed course 60 minutes for £20.

              .alert.alert-info
                p We encourage safe and responsible tanning in a supervised environment.

          .row.service-meta
            .cell-sm-2.mr
              img.img-responsive(src='img/tanning-protan.jpg', title='Tanning Pro Tan', alt='Tanning Pro Tan')

            .cell-sm
              h2.service-meta-title.
                Here at Suntrap we pride ourselves on providing the best tanning
                and products at affordable prices.

              .service-meta-content
                p.
                  Our wide range of protan accelaerator creams which
                  boost, enhance and prolong your tan whilst repairing and
                  replenishing the skin.

                .service-offer
                  p.service-offer-title Prices start at just £1.00

          .row.service-copy
            .cell-sm-6.mr
              img.img-responsive(src='img/tanning-urban-tan-add.jpg', title='UV Free Tanning by Urban Tan', alt='UV Free Tanning by Urban Tan')

            .cell-sm
              h2.service-copy-title UV Free Tanning

              .service-copy-content
                p.
                  If you prefer to tan without the UV, or you want perfect tan for
                  that special ocassion, our Urban Spray Tan is for you.

                p.
                  Urban Tan is the most natural looking, paraben and fragrance free,
                  sunless spray tan that dries in a minute.
                  It is the chosen product of celebrities &amp; make-up artists and
                  blends to suit every skin tone.

                p.
                  Our experienced and educated therapist will carry out a
                  consultation, carefully selecting and blending the required shade
                  before applying your flawless tan.

                .service-offer
                  p.service-offer-title Full Body Spray tan £17.00
